sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant FE as React Frontend
    participant NG as Nginx
    participant BE as Express Backend
    participant DB as MySQL
    participant FS as Firebase Storage

    Note over U,FS: Create Blog Post Flow
    U->>FE: Fill title, content, category
    U->>FE: Drag & drop cover image
    FE->>FS: Upload image to Firebase Storage
    FS-->>FE: Download URL
    FE->>NG: POST /api/blogs { title, content, categoryId, coverImage, status }
    NG->>BE: Proxy request
    BE->>BE: authenticate middleware (verify JWT)
    BE->>BE: validate middleware (Zod schema)
    BE->>DB: Verify category exists
    BE->>BE: generateUniqueSlug(title)
    BE->>BE: calculateReadTime(content)
    BE->>DB: INSERT blog + BlogCategory
    DB-->>BE: Blog record
    BE-->>NG: { blog }
    NG-->>FE: Response
    FE-->>U: Redirect to blog

    Note over U,DB: Like / Bookmark Blog Flow
    U->>FE: Click bookmark icon
    FE->>NG: POST /api/blogs/:id/bookmark
    NG->>BE: Proxy request
    BE->>BE: authenticate middleware
    BE->>DB: Toggle Bookmark (insert or delete)
    DB-->>BE: bookmarked: true/false
    BE-->>NG: { bookmarked }
    NG-->>FE: Response
    FE-->>U: Update bookmark icon state

    Note over U,DB: Comment on Blog Flow
    U->>FE: Type comment, click submit
    FE->>NG: POST /api/blogs/:slug/comments
    NG->>BE: Proxy request
    BE->>BE: authenticate middleware
    BE->>DB: INSERT comment (with optional parentId)
    DB-->>BE: Comment record
    BE-->>NG: { comment }
    NG-->>FE: Response
    FE-->>U: Render new comment in thread
